Usage <br/><br/>
bury &lt;item&gt;     this will bury one item<br/>
bury all        this will bury all in the room<br/>
bury all.&lt;item&gt; this will bury all item by that name in the<br/>
                       room and inventory. use at own risk :)<br/>
<br/>
Bury an item, you were carrying in the dust. When an item is buried,<br/>
you cannot see it directly, but have to dig to find it.<br/>
